title: Doha Tower Fit-Out — Project Plan
summary: Levels 15-22 interior fit-out · 180 days · Target completion 2026-12-15
meta: | type: project_plan | ref: PP-2026-014 | date: 2026-06-24

section: Project Overview
text: Complete interior fit-out of office floors 15-22 for Qatar Holding. Scope includes civil, MEP, finishes, joinery, and furniture.

